DCL --> Data Control Language

DCL --> deals with the permission

like DDL, DCL will also have two implicit commit and will be executed in same manner as in case of DDL


Commands:

GRANT
REVOKE
SET ROLE


For Every operation in SQL we require permissions from DBA. This is done by DCL commands.
Every DCL commands have inplicit commit like DDL commands.


Privilages:


    1. System Privilages --> applicable only for application developers and Adminstrators.
    2. Object Privilages --> object privilages are granted by Schema Owner.
